OL,3,C'Vital' Somerset bus routes saved from
OL,4,Cbeing axed
OL,6,FA number of 'vital' bus routes in that
OL,7,Fwere at risk of being axed have been
OL,8,Fsaved.
OL,10,FThe decision to continue the 58, 54,
OL,11,F28, and 25 services was made after a
OL,12,Fdeal was struck between the council
OL,13,Fand Buses of Somerset.
OL,15,F, who said it would be a 'disaster' if
OL,16,Fthey were cut.
OL,18,FMany of them relied on the services to
OL,19,Fget to work, doctor appointments, and
OL,20,Fthe shops.
