OL,3,C'Vital' Somerset bus routes saved from
OL,4,Cbeing axed
OL,6,FSomerset Council will now continue to
OL,7,Ffund routes 54 and 25, between Taunton
OL,8,Fand Yeovil and Taunton and Dulverton,
OL,9,Fand First Bus will run the 58, between
OL,10,FYeovil and Wincanton, and the 28,
OL,11,Fbetween Taunton and Minehead, without
OL,12,Fa subsidy.
OL,14,FThe new deal means the routes will be
OL,15,Fsecured until at least March 2025.
