OL,3,C'Vital' Somerset bus routes saved from
OL,4,Cbeing axed
OL,6,FCouncillor Richard Wilkins, Somerset
OL,7,FCouncil's Lead Member for Transport
OL,8,Fand Digital said: "We know how
OL,9,Fimportant these services are for
OL,10,Fpeople and we've recently seen the
OL,11,Fstrength of feeling around ensuring
OL,12,Fthey are protected.
OL,14,F"Passenger numbers have been rising,
OL,15,Fwhich is positive, this trend still
OL,16,Fneeds to continue to ensure the long-
OL,17,Fterm future of the routes.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
