OL,3,C'Vital' Somerset bus routes saved from
OL,4,Cbeing axed
OL,6,F"The message to everyone is please do
OL,7,Fkeep using and valuing these services,
OL,8,Fand we will continue to work with
OL,9,FBuses of Somerset and Somerset Bus
OL,10,FPartnership to promote bus travel."
OL,12,FJames Eustace, Commercial Director at
OL,13,FFirst Bus South which operates Buses
OL,14,Fof Somerset, added: "Reducing or
OL,15,Fwithdrawing services is the last thing
OL,16,Fwe want to do, so we're delighted to
OL,17,Fhave found a solution with Somerset
OL,18,FCouncil that allows the four routes to
OL,19,Fcontinue to run.
