OL,3,C'Vital' Somerset bus routes saved from
OL,4,Cbeing axed
OL,6,F"While running these services remains
OL,7,Fcommercially challenging, we
OL,8,Funderstand how valued the services
OL,9,Fare, which is why we've agreed to
OL,10,Fsupport the local community and
OL,11,Fcontinue to run the 28 and 58 routes
OL,12,Fwithout financial assistance.
OL,14,F"However, we need to be clear that for
OL,15,Fbus services to continue operating in
OL,16,Fthe long term they need to continually
OL,17,Fbe commercially sustainable and cover
OL,18,Ftheir cost of operations.
